headline: POTTERY BARN LAUNCHES COLLABORATION WITH ROLLER RABBIT
summary: SAN FRANCISCO, August 08, 2025--Pottery Barn, a portfolio brand of Williams-Sonoma, Inc. (NYSE: WSM), the world’s largest digital-first, design-led and sustainable home retailer, announced today, a new home collaboration with vibrant fashion and lifestyle brand, Roller Rabbit. Roller Rabbit’s new partnership with Pottery Barn builds upon Roller Rabbit’s existing popular home furnishing collections with both the Pottery Barn Kids and Pottery Barn Teen brands.
